data.description: Enjoy acreage living with access to Hwy 75! This home was completely remodeled and boasts the open floor plan on the main floor that is so desired! New, gorgeous kitchen, main floor laundry, main floor bedroom/office and updated main floor full bathroom. Upstairs you will find three additional bedrooms and a bathroom. Newer HVAC with allergen eliminator, roof, windows, plumbing and wiring make this home like new! Sellers have preserved the charm of an 1880's home with the updates you desire today! This is a beautiful home with the acres ready for your animals or the most amazing space for the family to enjoy!
